    <title>Blog Starter</title>
    <link href="/2023/08/30/blog-starter/"/>
    <url>/2023/08/30/blog-starter/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="blog-with-Hexo"><a href="#blog-with-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="blog with Hexo"></a>blog with Hexo</h2><h3 id="installation-and-setup"><a href="#installation-and-setup" class="headerlink" title="installation and setup"></a>installation and setup</h3><blockquote><p>ref: <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/num_001/article/details/126370104">https://blog.csdn.net/num_001/article/details/126370104</a></p><p><a href="http://www.taodudu.cc/news/show-5247386.html?action=onClick">http://www.taodudu.cc/news/show-5247386.html?action=onClick</a></p></blockquote><h4 id="install-NodeJS"><a href="#install-NodeJS" class="headerlink" title="install NodeJS"></a>install NodeJS</h4><p>choose a early LTS version of nodejs: <a href="https://nodejs.org/download/release/v14.21.3/">https://nodejs.org/download/release/v14.21.3/</a></p><p>move to somewhere for applications like: &#x2F;usr&#x2F;opt and link it to &#x2F;usr&#x2F;bin as:</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">sudo <span class="hljs-built_in">ln</span> -s /usr/local/node-v8.9.3-linux-x64/bin/node /usr/local/bin/node <br>sudo <span class="hljs-built_in">ln</span> -s /usr/local/node-v8.9.3-linux-x64/bin/npm  /usr/local/bin/npm<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># test if success</span><br>npm -v<br>node -v<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>then we have <code>npm</code> and <code>node</code></p><h4 id="install-hexo-using-npm"><a href="#install-hexo-using-npm" class="headerlink" title="install hexo using npm"></a>install hexo using npm</h4><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh">npm install -g hexo-cli --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># test</span><br>hexo<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># link hexo if test failed</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">ln</span> -s /usr/local/node-v8.9.3-linux-x64/lib/node_modules/hexo-cli/bin/hexo /usr/bin/hexo<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>now we have <code>hexo</code></p><h3 id="create-hexo-blog-website-with-local-directory"><a href="#create-hexo-blog-website-with-local-directory" class="headerlink" title="create hexo blog website with local directory"></a>create hexo blog website with local directory</h3><blockquote><p>see ref: <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/github-pages.html#%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/github-pages.html#%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2</a></p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment">## create a desired folder at proper place and do initiation</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> blog_hexo<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> blog_hexo<br>hexo init<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># change npm source if initiation failed</span><br>npm config <span class="hljs-built_in">set</span> registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">## start server and visit it via local port</span><br>hexo server<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>then we can start edit blog using <code>hexo</code></p><figure class="highlight applescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs applescript"><span class="hljs-comment">## github deployer</span><br>npm install hexo-deployer-git <span class="hljs-comment">--save</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>in file <code>_config.yml</code>, change <code>deploy</code> part as:</p><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dts"><span class="hljs-symbol">deploy:</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  type:</span> git<br><span class="hljs-symbol">  repository:</span> https:<span class="hljs-comment">//github.com/&lt;username&gt;/&lt;project&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-meta"># example, https:<span class="hljs-comment">//github.com/hexojs/hexojs.github.io</span></span><br>  <span class="hljs-meta"># git@github.com:hexojs/hexojs.github.io.git</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  branch:</span> master<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>Note:  github now only supports key login, so generate your local ssh&#x2F;gpg key and use ssh repo address like: <a href="mailto:&#103;&#105;&#x74;&#x40;&#x67;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#117;&#x62;&#46;&#x63;&#x6f;&#109;">&#103;&#105;&#x74;&#x40;&#x67;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#117;&#x62;&#46;&#x63;&#x6f;&#109;</a>:hexojs&#x2F;hexojs.github.io.git</strong></p><p><code>Tips:</code> seems github.io only supports lower-case url</p><h3 id="blog-finetune"><a href="#blog-finetune" class="headerlink" title="blog finetune"></a>blog finetune</h3><ul><li>theme</li></ul><p>using <a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid</a>, with its <a href="https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/docs/start/">start-up manual</a></p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sh"><span class="hljs-comment"># generate blog</span><br>hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy<br><span class="hljs-comment"># see the outcome immediately on local host</span><br>hexo server<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Tips for using theme Fluid</p><figure class="highlight verilog"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs verilog"># <span class="hljs-keyword">generate</span> `about` page when using at first <span class="hljs-keyword">time</span><br>hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> page about<br><br># then modify `/source/about/index<span class="hljs-variable">.md</span>`<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>fluid cheatsheet</code></p><ul><li><p>abstract</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml">contetns as abstract<br><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- more --&gt;</span><br>contents left<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>Front-matter settings of single article</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html">---title: titleauthor: authortags: [tag1, tag2] # tagsindex_img: /img/img.jpg # cover image in /source/img/example.jpg or urlbanner_img: /img/post_banner.jpg # article specific bannerbanner_img_height: 60banner_mask_alpha: 0.5date: YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS # timeexcerpt: abstract # abstract contenthide: true # if private articlesticky: 100 # if stick at top, bigger toppercomment: &#x27;valine&#x27; # whether to use commentsmath: true # if needs formula showuplayout: about # page layout---# front setup<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="language-css">  <span class="hljs-comment">/* whole page font setup */</span>  <span class="hljs-selector-tag">html</span>, <span class="hljs-selector-tag">body</span>, <span class="hljs-selector-class">.markdown-body</span> &#123;    <span class="hljs-attribute">font-family</span>: KaiTi,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;</span>,Georgia, sans, serif;    <span class="hljs-attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="hljs-number">15px</span>;  &#125;  <span class="hljs-comment">/* markdown font only */</span>  <span class="hljs-selector-class">.markdown-body</span> &#123;    <span class="hljs-attribute">font-family</span>: KaiTi,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;</span>,Georgia, sans, serif;    <span class="hljs-attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="hljs-number">15px</span>;  &#125;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">style</span>&gt;</span>contents# footera line need footer<sup id="fnref:1" class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn:1" rel="footnote"><span class="hint--top hint--rounded" aria-label="footer 1# note&#123;% note noteName %&#125; # noteName: primary, secondary, success, danger, warning, info, lightnote content&#123;% endnote %&#125;# in-line label&#123;% label labelname @text %&#125; # labelName: primary default info success warning danger# checkbox&#123;% cb text, checked?, incline? %&#125; # ?: false or true, e.g. &#123;% cb text, true, true %&#125;; incline for whether break lines# button&#123;% btn url, text, title %&#125; url: link url, text: text shown in button, title: text shown on mouseover# graph set&#123;% gi total n1-n2-... %&#125; # total: total graph number, n1...: graph each line![](url)...&#123;% endgi%&#125;">[1]</span></a></sup>- generating new custom page:  <hexoPostRenderCodeBlock><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">hexo new page customPageName<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>then edit <code>/source/customPageName/index.md</code></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html"># if need markdown<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span> <span class="hljs-attr">class</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;markdown-body&quot;</span>&gt;</span>contents<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">div</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><section class="footnotes"><div class="footnote-list"><ol><li><span id="fn:1" class="footnote-text"><span>footer 1# note&amp;#123;% note noteName %&amp;#125; # noteName: primary, secondary, success, danger, warning, info, lightnote content&amp;#123;% endnote %&amp;#125;# in-line label&amp;#123;% label labelname @text %&amp;#125; # labelName: primary default info success warning danger# checkbox&amp;#123;% cb text, checked?, incline? %&amp;#125; # ?: false or true, e.g. &amp;#123;% cb text, true, true %&amp;#125;; incline for whether break lines# button&amp;#123;% btn url, text, title %&amp;#125; url: link url, text: text shown in button, title: text shown on mouseover# graph set&amp;#123;% gi total n1-n2-… %&amp;#125; # total: total graph number, n1…: graph each line<img src="/url">…&amp;#123;% endgi%&amp;#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></hexoPostRenderCodeBlock><a href="#fnref:1" rev="footnote" class="footnote-backref"> ↩</a></span></span></li></ol></div></section>]]></content>
    
    
    
